          "SAMPLE": [
            {
              "pointer": "",
              "coded_information": null,
              "free_text": [
                "Prepared from a spec pure polycrystalline Germanium",
                "in fine powder form (grain size less than 10**(-4) cm.",
                "The spectroscopic analysis of the used element showed",
                "the presence of some impurities of low total cross",
                "sections (Si: 15 ppm and less than 10 ppm for S, Ca,",
                "Cr and Fe). The Germanium powder is packed in perspex",
                "container with glass windows. One sample of thickness",
                "2.90 gm/cm**2 corresponding to about 0.80 transmission",
                "for 0.0253 eV neutron was prepared. For incident",
                "intensity measurements, a glass plate of the same",
                "thickness has been used to eliminate the effect of the",
                "lateral glass plates of the container. Germanium has",
                "a diamond type structure crystallised in the cubic",
                "system with cell edge a0 = 5.6576 Angstrom and related",
                "to the space group 9OH - FD3M.8 atoms are present per",
                "unit cell of coordinates (0, 0, 0, 1/4, 1/4, 1/4)."
              ]
            }
          ],
          "MONITOR": [
            {
