          ],
          "COMMENT": [
            {
              "pointer": "",
              "coded_information": null,
              "free_text": [
                "Given data is in good agreement with the value 8.50 b",
                "of Shull,C.G., E.O.Wollan: Phys. Rev. 81(1950) 527 in",
                "Neutron Diffraction and Transmission Studies as well as",
                "with the value of (8.6 +- 0.50) b reported in Neutron",
                "Cross-Sections, AECU 2040 (1952).",
                "  Using sig(a) = (2.23 +- 0.18) b of Pomerance,H.:",
                "Phys. Rev. 83 (1951) 641 - 645 in pile oscillator",
                "measurements, sig(s) = (7.46 +- 0.16) b was obtained",
                "and good agreement with (7.5 +- 0.20) b of Second",
                "International Conference on Nuclear Data for Reactors,",
                "Conf. Proc. vol. 1(1970) Helsinki and is slightly",
                "lower than 9.0 b of Hughes,D.J., R.Schwartz: Neutron",
                "Cross-Sections. BNL - 325, 2nd. Edition (1958),",
                "Supplement (1960) and Supplement no. 2 (1966)"
              ]
            }
          ],
