          "COMMENT": [
            {
              "pointer": "",
              "coded_information": null,
              "free_text": [
                "Given data was obtained by using",
                "sig(a) = (2.23 +- 0.18) b of Pomerance,H.: Phys. Rev.",
                "83(1951) 641-645. Given data is in good agreement",
                "with (7.5 +- 0.2) b of Mughabghab,S.F., D.I.Garber:",
                "BNL - 325 (1976), however disagree with (3 +- 1) b of",
